  <brief_title>Study to Find Optimal Dose of Local Spinal Anesthetic (Mepivacaine) Combined With Narcotic (Fentanyl) For Knee Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimal Dose of Spinal Mepivacaine Combined With Fentanyl For Knee Arthroscopy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
